No. 42,

October Term, 1952.

F. W. Woolworth Co. v. Contemporary Arts, Inc., Cedric W. Porter *811and Harry F. R. Dolan were on the motion for respondent. Kenneth W. Greenawalt and Martin A. Schenck were on the brief for petitioner in opposition to the motion.

*810344 U. S. 228. The motion for clarification of the mandate is denied.

The Chief Justice and Mr. Justice Harlan took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
